==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Greenback
<hw>Green"back"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of the legal
tender notes of the United States; a note of paper currency of the
United States; -- first issued in 1862, and having the devices on the
back printed with green ink, to prevent alterations and
counterfeits.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Greenbacker</ent>⟦br⟧
